## Algorithm Complexity Summary

| Algorithm | Complexity | Triggered By | GreenTech Role |
|-----------|-----------|--------------|----------------|
| MCMF (SPFA) | O(V·E·F) | Run Distribution | Optimal energy routing |
| Dijkstra | O((V+E) log V) | Zone click | Priority-aware pathfinding |
| BFS | O(V+E) | Fault injection | Fault impact detection |
| DFS | O(V+E) | Fault injection | Subgraph isolation |
| Bellman-Ford | O(V·E) | Fault injection | Stress cycle detection |
| Topological Sort | O(V+E) | Stress cycle | Load shedding order |
| Segment Tree | O(log n) | Every run | Zone load range queries |
| Fenwick Tree | O(log n) | Every run | CO₂ accounting |
| Union-Find | O(α(V)) | Fault/reroute | Connectivity verification |
| Max-Heap | O(log n) | Prediction | Failure prediction |
| Min-Heap | O(log n) | Distribution | Source load balancing |
| Adaptive Updates | O(E) | Every run | Self-learning routing |

